<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

82
00:06:49,630 --> 00:06:51,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini adalah anggur poppi.</font>

83
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Setiap dua minggu,</font>

84
00:06:55,330 --> 00:06:59,600
<font color=#FFFF00>kalau kau tidak meminum lagi anggur poppi ini,</font>

85
