101
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berjanji.</font>

102
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:36,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan!</font>

103
00:08:38,930 --> 00:08:40,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan, Doryongnim!</font>

104
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:42,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan, Jeoha!</font>

105
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:48,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang yang membunuh ayahku...</font>

106
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,760
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukan Jeoha, aku sudah tahu.</font>

107
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:54,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kumohon,</font>

108
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:57,730
<font color=#FFFF00>tolong jangan meminumnya.</font>

109
00:08:58,130 --> 00:09:01,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kecuali kau ingin melihatnya mati duluan,</font>

110
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,800
<font color=#FFFF00>cepat minum anggur poppi itu!</font>

111
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:08,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha, kumohon.</font>

112
00:09:33,430 --> 00:09:34,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebutkan namamu!</font>

113
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

114
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:44,870
