115
00:09:47,330 --> 00:09:48,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Yi Sun.</font>

116
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:01,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Darah?</font>

117
00:10:01,370 --> 00:10:02,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Khusus untukmu,</font>

118
00:10:04,460 --> 00:10:06,830
<font color=#FFFF00>aku memberi tiga pil poppi.</font>

119
00:10:09,130 --> 00:10:11,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu cukup untuk membuat orang ketergantungan,</font>

120
00:10:12,730 --> 00:10:13,760
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi tiga...</font>

121
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:17,160
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan menghabisinya di tempat.</font>

122
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:22,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

123
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:24,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok.</font>

124
00:10:25,830 --> 00:10:26,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Rencanamu...</font>

125
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:31,030
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah membunuhku.</font>

126
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:41,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah aku tampak seperti monster bagimu?</font>

127
00:10:44,330 --> 00:10:45,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

128
00:10:45,930 --> 00:10:48,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Dunia yang kita tinggali ini,</font>

129
00:10:49,830 --> 00:10:52,400
<font color=#FFFF00>merupakan pusaran api,
dan aku berusaha bertahan.</font>

130
00:10:53,060 --> 00:10:56,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebuah negeri yang mendorong rakyatnya sendiri...</font>

131
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:57,900
