<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

138
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:25,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak!</font>

139
00:11:44,330 --> 00:11:48,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Se--sejak saat pertama kali bertemu denganmu,</font>

140
00:11:50,830 --> 00:11:51,900
<font color=#FFFF00>aku...</font>

141
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:56,400
<font color=#FFFF00>...se--segenap hatiku...</font>

142
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:00,460
<font color=#FFFF00>...hanya mencintaimu.</font>

143
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:21,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak boleh.</font>

144
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim.</font>

145
00:12:27,230 --> 00:12:28,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim.</font>

146
