<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim!</font>

148
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:36,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak! Tidak!</font>

149
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:38,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim!</font>

150
00:12:45,100 --> 00:12:46,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim!</font>

151
00:12:53,130 --> 00:12:56,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwa Gun-ah, dari mana saja kau?</font>

152
00:12:56,500 --> 00:12:58,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Ritualnya Seja sudah berakhir.</font>

153
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:00,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

154
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:03,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak mungkin. Katanya ritualnya pukul 11 malam.</font>

155
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Abeoji. Jeoha di mana?</font>

156
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:11,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha ada di mana?</font>

157
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:15,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak melihatnya lagi setelah ritual.</font>

158
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:46,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Gon-ah.</font>

159
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:50,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah kau sekarang...</font>

160
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:53,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...masih orangku?</font>

161
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:01,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang...</font>

162
00:14:02,930 --> 00:14:04,960
<font color=#FFFF00>...apa kau masih orangku atau tidak?</font>

163
00:14:05,300 --> 00:14:06,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya...</font>

164
00:14:08,730 --> 00:14:10,000
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah orang Aghassi.</font>

165
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau...</font>

166
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:15,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...berbohong padaku?</font>

167
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:17,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila saya tidak melakukannya,</font>

168
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:22,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi akan terluka.</font>

169
00:14:26,260 --> 00:14:27,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji...</font>

170
00:14:28,530 --> 00:14:29,800
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengatakannya padamu?</font>

171
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:32,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

172
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji...</font>

173
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...membunuh Jeoha?</font>

