181
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:33,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat.</font>

182
00:15:33,730 --> 00:15:34,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Busang.</font>

183
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:38,260
