185
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:44,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Mama.</font>

186
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:49,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Mohon jaga dan bimbing putri saya.</font>

187
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:53,400
